com.theif519.sakoverlay.Core.Async

Class FloatingFragmentDeserializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • com.theif519.sakoverlay.Core.Async.FloatingFragmentDeserializer

  • public abstract class FloatingFragmentDeserializer
extends <any>
    Created by theif519 on 10/31/2015.

    A simple, yet very powerful utilities which converts serialized key-value pairs into ArrayMaps. JSONObjects get turned into ArrayMaps, and the root, JSONArray, is the actual mapList.
